    "description": "<strong>Deck-Building Card Battle!</strong><br>An Rrealtime-style card game that you can easily play with a deck of 10 cards and simple rules.<br><br>Card battles that progress in real time!<br>Build a deck of your choice and fight through the battle!<br><br>With over 100 different cards, use a variety of skills to hunt down your enemies!<br>In a world where humans are turned into cards, can you survive and take revenge?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play image</h2>The game has two parts: the story part and the battle part.<br>While following the story and pursuing the truth of the cards, you will use the cards to defeat the pursuers and other enemies sent by the empire.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Combat</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252290/extras/1c57361a6e951c9015b8051ba2a84193.avif?t=1738426279\" width=400 height=224 /></span><br><br>Ancient Sacrifice is a deck-building card game that progresses in real time. Combat progresses in real time, so there is no time to think carefully as in most card games.<br><br>Do you put together only strong cards and push through with power? <br>Or do you play strong cards at the expense of easy cards? <br><br>It is up to you to decide what strategy to use when building your deck.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252290/extras/dfee0823f3d84f2a938456bb254aa0c9.avif?t=1738426279\" width=400 height=224 /></span><br><br><strong>Over 40 skills! </strong><br><strong>Over 100 cards! </strong><br><br>Find your own optimal solution from a wide range of card options.<br><br>Take advantage of the battle by paying attention to the speed and amount of mana recovery, which varies depending on the map.<br><br><strong>My Card</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252290/extras/1f070eb9ba88d4856c8ba9334015e9a7.avif?t=1738426279\" width=400 height=224 /></span><br>[My Card] is unlocked in the mid-game.<br>Allows you to create a card to your liking by acquiring skills.<br>Create a card that suits your deck with your own hands!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Worldview</h2>A world where cards have power.<br>The empire sacrifices lives to generate cards, and by harnessing the power of the cards, it hopes to maintain peace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252290/extras/372e6b65f3a67dc1b647ea368de4fb6b.avif?t=1738426279\" width=400 height=208 /></span><br><br>The story begins when Amelia Malerin, whose father is a card smith, is entrusted by her father with a card that has been passed down in the family.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Musics an Arts</h2>Arts: Midjourney<br><br>Musics: Peritune / 効果音ラボ<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Streaming Guidelines</h2>Individuals and corporations can stream without prior permission.",
